{"tid":2511584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青島海域貨輪相撞數百噸油洩漏 污染情況不明","createTime":"2021-05-01T04:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T09:33:49.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"574c8c213d085fda74ff53dd3165229c09e9408b","tid":2511584,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"青島海域貨輪相撞數百噸油洩漏 污染情況不明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/4/29/n12914477.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F21%2F4%2F29%2Fn12914477.htm&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=24c0ca33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/4/29/n12914477.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i-epochtimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2021/04/id12914495-0034c2ttly1gq0kpfo712j60fk0ezwf902.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi-epochtimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fid12914495-0034c2ttly1gq0kpfo712j60fk0ezwf902.jpg&h=942c8e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2021年04月30日訊】（大紀元記者張玉潔綜合報導）4月27日，青島海域兩艘外籍貨輪相撞，造成數百噸油洩漏事件，目前中國方面說正在進行處理，但沒有說明處理進度，相關海域污染情況也不明朗。<br />\n<br />\n山東海事局4月28日發微博稱，4月27日上午9時在青島海域，兩艘外籍貨輪相撞&mdash;&mdash;巴拿馬籍雜貨船「義海」輪（SEA JUSTICE）與利比里亞籍錨泊油船「交響樂」輪（A SYMPHONY）在山東青島朝連島東南海域發生碰撞，碰撞導致油船一貨艙受損，海面發現「少量」溢油，無人員傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n4月29日，山東海事局再次發微博稱，船舶溢油入海量為400噸左右，事發海域距青島港約40海里（約75公里）。<br />\n<br />\n但一位匿名的山東海事局官員向路透社透露，初步估計有大約500噸或3420桶油洩露至黃海，但還需要進一步評估。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2021/04/id12914497-0034c2ttly1gq0kpfnrslj60jg0bk0ti02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fid12914497-0034c2ttly1gq0kpfnrslj60jg0bk0ti02.jpg&h=5dc67548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，「交響樂」號油輪當時停泊在青島港，運載了大約100萬桶瀝青混合料，當天能見度不足200公尺。此次漏油事件引起外界對青島港運輸中斷和海洋污染的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述船舶管理公司Goodwood Ship Management一位經理的電郵內容表示，撞船發生在青島當地時間早上8時50分，「撞擊導致左舷前側受力，貨油艙和壓載艙破損，大量的油流入海中」。<br />\n<br />\n中共生態環境部的一名官員28日告訴路透社，他們已經派專家前往青島檢查溢油情況，但該官員沒有提供進一步的細節。<br />\n<br />\n目前，事故發生現場周圍半徑10海里的水域範圍內禁止船舶駛入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZTHZ61DatSymP2j1qpa55rc9nhYLWukjvDHQ2ofKTCAy?filename=cEQjp83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEQjp83.png&h=057a5f9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"138bc7421a5b1c1bcd19bf65a70715266a1c5c10","tid":2511584,"uid":353256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:40:40.000Z","msg":"有毒氣體對人員無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f4bc7a9fe7decd13648c9669fde1db74963328","tid":2511584,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf55dc78d02ffa616234d47e747cf228448388d3","tid":2511584,"uid":287891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"之前仲笑鳩人倒核廢料<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3968544eaf63c5ea40f5f3f9e7def237a557f564","tid":2511584,"uid":43173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bf55dc78d02ffa616234d47e747cf228448388d3","tid":2511584,"uid":287891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"之前仲笑鳩人倒核廢料<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"青海就係下水道嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b87872e339ad0856dca27299db99771d659f34c","tid":2511584,"uid":385411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"咁耐都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa3e316d8ce6d3d97fbb2b870fc487a3308b119","tid":2511584,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}